Identifiers must be unique by the first 8 characters, case-insensitive.

Do not use git

Grep only in files *.p2c and *.cc

Do not look into any subdirectory except tests/

base.pas is retired: work.p2c is the compiler source, base.cc is its
host-native mirror. Change them together; do not modify base.pas.

In work.p2c, use constants false and true for int variables with Boolean meaning.

Line length in work.p2c must not exceed 128 characters.

Output of test programs is all uppercase.

The input language is case-insensitive.

Do not increase time limits in shell scripts.

Do not commit compiler changes until `make check` (self-host fixpoint) and
./runtests.sh -work pass.

Before modifying work.p2c or base.cc, save the known good state for ease of
reverting if needed.
